response.overview: A caring daughter, a laid-back mother, a popular teacher, a wife you are thick as thieves with – Joanna – is outstanding in each of these roles. But in none of them does she feel like herself. That is why she leads a double life. She has a secret she shares with no-one.
response.title: My Wonderful Life

crew.name: Julia Bogusławska
crew.job: Executive In Charge Of Post Production
